In this part, you'll set up Chef server and Chef Automate, each on its own server. You'll also set up your workstation to work with these systems.

If you're new to Chef, you might consider first working through this tutorial [using hosted Chef](/tutorials/manage-a-node/rhel/hosted/) to understand how Chef server works. You can then come back and install Chef server and Chef Automate in your environment.

