## 2. Bring up systems to run Chef Automate and Chef server

Chef Automate and Chef server can run on several Linux distrubutions.

Start by reviewing the [platform](https://docs.chef.io/install_chef_automate.html#platforms) and  [infrastructure](https://docs.chef.io/install_chef_automate.html#infrastructure) requirements for Chef Automate and Chef server. For this tutorial, you don't need to configure build nodes.

